     H            Y.
     F** ADKR33 **********************************
     F*臨時かんばんオーダーファイル作成
     F*    KATOGI.         2015.12.16            *
     F********************************************
     FADKWP32 IF  E                    DISK
     FADKPP31 O   E                    DISK                      A
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C                     TIME           WDATE
      *
     C                     READ ADKWP321                 80
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'
     C           W2SHN1    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     EXSR #SB500
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ ADKWP321                 80
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *--------------------------------------*
      *                                      *
      *--------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB500    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARADKPP311
     C                     Z-ADDSDATE     D3KOHZ
     C                     Z-ADDSTIME     D3KOTI
     C                     MOVELW#PGM     D3KOME
     C                     MOVELW2SHN1    D3SHN1
